---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Restaurant Marketing in Scarborough | Toronto Restaurant Growth"
  description="Scarborough restaurant marketing that drives real results. We help Tamil, Caribbean, Bangladeshi, and global cuisine restaurants get found on Google and packed with local diners."
>

  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
    <nav style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #f5f5f0; font-size: 0.85rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Home</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      <a href="/locations/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Locations</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      Restaurant Marketing Scarborough
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 100px 24px 80px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Scarborough, Toronto</p>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Restaurant Marketing in Scarborough</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #ccc; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px;">
          Scarborough has one of the most authentic, underrated food scenes in Canada — your restaurant deserves to be found by the people already searching for it.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #E85D04; color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LOCAL SCENE -->
    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">The Local Food Scene</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Scarborough's Restaurant Scene Is the Real Thing</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          If you've eaten along Lawrence Avenue East on a Friday evening, you already know: Scarborough's Tamil and Sri Lankan corridor is one of the most concentrated stretches of authentic South Asian cuisine anywhere in North America. The smell of freshly made roti, the sizzle of kottu, the slow-cooked curries that take all day — this is food rooted in culture, not trend.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          But the Tamil corridor is just the beginning. Drive north through Scarborough and you move through waves of Bangladeshi restaurants in Flemingdon Park's orbit, Caribbean spots in Malvern and Morningside, and Chinese restaurants that have been feeding the community for decades. Scarborough Junction has a scrappy, neighbourhood-first dining energy that chains can't replicate.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          What's happening in Scarborough's food scene right now is something special: second-generation restaurant owners who grew up watching their parents cook are starting to open their own places. They're bringing modern presentation to traditional recipes, experimenting with fusion, and finding audiences hungry for exactly what they're doing.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          The challenge these restaurants face is visibility. A phenomenal roti spot tucked into a plaza on Markham Road can be invisible to someone sitting three kilometres away who just searched "roti near me" on Google. That's the gap we fill.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DELIVERABLES -->
    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">What We Do</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">What We Do For Scarborough Restaurants</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          We build the digital presence your restaurant deserves, specific to how Scarborough diners actually find and choose where to eat.
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin-top: 28px;">
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Google Maps Domination:</strong> We optimize your Google Business Profile for Scarborough-specific searches — including cuisine-specific terms in Tamil, Bangla, and Patois communities — and build the review velocity that pushes you to the top of local results.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Scarborough-Specific SEO:</strong> We target neighbourhood-level keywords like "best Sri Lankan food Scarborough," "halal restaurant Lawrence Ave East," and "Bangladeshi biryani near Markham Road" — terms your ideal customers are actually typing.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Local Food Blogger Outreach:</strong> We connect you with Scarborough and GTA food bloggers including Dished Toronto, Toronto Eats, and community Instagram accounts with 10K–100K followers who authentically cover your neighbourhood's food scene.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Social Media That Shows the Food:</strong> Short-form video content for Instagram and TikTok tailored to Scarborough's audience — not generic food content, but videos that capture the story behind your dishes and the neighbourhood you're part of.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Google Ads for Scarborough Searches:</strong> Targeted paid campaigns for high-intent Scarborough searches during peak hours. We spend your ad dollars where they convert, not where they look impressive on a report.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Monthly Reporting You Can Read:</strong> No jargon. Every month you get: how many people found you on Google, how many clicked to call or get directions, what reviews came in, and what we're doing next.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HALAL CALLOUT -->
    <section style="background: #1B4332; color: #fff; padding: 64px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <span style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Halal Restaurant Community</span>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Serving Scarborough's Halal Restaurant Community</h2>
        <p style="color: #a7c4b5; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Scarborough is home to one of Toronto's largest Muslim communities, and the halal dining scene here reflects that richness. From Bangladeshi biryani shops to Somali restaurants in the north end to South Asian halal fast-casual spots — this is a market that deserves dedicated marketing strategy, not a generic approach.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #a7c4b5; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          We understand how halal restaurant customers discover new spots: through community WhatsApp groups, halal food review pages on Instagram, and trusted Google searches for "halal near me" in specific Scarborough neighbourhoods.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #a7c4b5;">
          Learn more: <a href="/niche/halal-restaurant-marketing-toronto/" style="color: #5ee7a0;">Halal Restaurant Marketing Toronto →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Questions</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">How much does restaurant marketing cost in Scarborough?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Our Scarborough restaurant marketing packages start at $497/month for Google Maps optimization and local SEO. Full-service packages including paid ads and social media run $997–$1,997/month depending on the scope. Book a free audit and we'll tell you exactly what your restaurant needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">Do you work with restaurants outside Scarborough?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Yes — we serve restaurants across the GTA including <a href="/locations/restaurant-marketing-brampton/" style="color: #E85D04;">Brampton</a>, North York, Mississauga, Markham, and downtown Toronto. Scarborough is one of our core markets given the incredible diversity of the food scene here.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">Can you help Tamil and Sri Lankan restaurants rank on Google?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Absolutely. We have deep experience with the Tamil and South Asian dining corridor along Lawrence Ave E. We understand how customers search — whether that's "kottu roti near me" or "best crab curry Scarborough" — and we build your Google presence around those real searches.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">How long before I see results?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Google Maps improvements typically show traction in 60–90 days. Organic search rankings for competitive terms can take 4–6 months to climb meaningfully. We'll set realistic benchmarks from day one and report on them monthly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- NEARBY CITIES -->
    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Also Serving</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Restaurant Marketing Across the GTA</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">We work with restaurants throughout Toronto and the surrounding area. Explore our other location pages:</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">North York</a>
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Markham</a>
          <a href="/locations/restaurant-marketing-brampton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Brampton</a>
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Mississauga</a>
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Etobicoke</a>
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Hamilton</a>
          <a href="/locations/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Vaughan</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section style="background: #E85D04; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 28px;">
          Your Scarborough restaurant deserves to be found. Let's make it happen.
        </h2>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #E85D04; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
